<div class="title">Methamphetamine and Benzodiazepines</div>
<div class="substance">Methamphetamine & Benzodiazepines</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Overclocker&Exact=1">Overclocker</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Overclocker. "Methamphetamine and Benzodiazepines: An Experience with Methamphetamine & Benzodiazepines (exp9402)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 5, 2005. erowid.org/exp/9402</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
